import React from 'react'
import Abouttop from '../Component/About component/Abouttop'
import Otherslide from '../Component/Otherslide'
import Footer from '../Component/Footer'
import Aboutimg from '../Component/About component/Aboutimg'
import Aboutdecs from '../Component/About component/Aboutdecs'
import Labsteps from '../Component/Labsteps'
import Aboutowner from '../Component/About component/Aboutowner'
import Aboutteam from '../Component/About component/Aboutteam'
import Header from '../Component/Header'


function About() {
    return (
        <>
            
            <Otherslide />
            <Abouttop />
            <Aboutimg />
            <Aboutdecs />
            <Labsteps />
            <Aboutowner />
            <Aboutteam />
            <Otherslide />
            


        </>
    )
}

export default About
